description:
#GoodOmens is a 2019 series, which co-stars Jack Whitehall, Miranda Richardson and Michael McKean. This is a six-part television serial based on the 1990 novel Good Omens: The Nice and Accurate Prophecies of Agnes Nutter, Witch by Terry Pratchett and Neil Gaiman. The story follows an angel Aziraphale (Sheen) and a demon Crowley (Tennant) who team up to prevent the impending birth of Satan. Witness the final battle between heaven and hell as the unusual duo try to prevent the coming of the antichrist. Coming soon in HD only on Amazon Prime Video.
